# TPK OTP Cheat Sheet

> **THIS IS WORK IN PROGRESS!**

## Usage

### mix.exs

Append the following line to your mix.deps

```elixir
  {:tpk_otp, ~> "0.0"}
```

## GenServer

### SimpleServer

A `TPK.OTP.SimpleServer` defines some convenience functions to avoid GenServer boilerplate code.

```elixir
  use TPK.OTP.SimpleServer, __MODULE__
```
